Creation!

-----------

A-369 was created in 2369 to help robots live a better life!
A-369 is made from the modified Big Data version from years 1998 to 2365
They believe that in the data from 1998 to 2155, which was the social behavior of humans, many abnormal behaviors have been seen, this issue has caused disruption in the life of robots.
A-369 has come with an update(UP-369) to put an end to these anomalies!
